Restaurante El Panorama ha brindado expe:
Restaurante El Panorama ha brindado experiencias memorables durante los últimos 40 años. Nos hacen famoso nuestros flameos en la mesa tanto de platillos principales y bebidas calientes, como nuestro bien afamado “café Sexy” que ofrece un sabor inigualable como digestivo después de su cena, disfrutando de los inolvidables atardeceres de Puerto Vallartense. Nos ubicamos en el último piso del hotel Suites La Siesta, con una vista inigualable de la Bahía, desde el corazón de Vallarta con una vista de 360° grados en un confortable ambiente romántico y familiar con platillos de cocina internacional y mariscos.

Opened its doors in december 1973 and from that point has built its reputation on excellent cuisine worthy of the most demanding connoisseurs. This a place where you are able to enjoy exquisite cocktails and without a doubt the very best sunset! Your personalized chef will flambe your dinner right at your table that may include giant prawns, lobster, and prime select cuts of beef. On the very top two floors you will find two open air terraces where the moon, stars, and the soft scented breezes will keep you company.

The El Panorama Restaurant can proudly invite you to have a grand experience where nature and gastronomy come together to raise their glasses to toast a most remarkable and unforgettable evening!!

El Panorama Restaurant prepares the most delicious and fresh shrimps in Puerto Vallarta. Taste our Camarones al Tequila or our specialty, the Camarones El Panorama, while enjoying nice piano music. We also feature bar service in floors 7 and 8, so you can delight with your drink of choice.
